  "decision_conditions": [
    "The development by reason of its design, siting and scale would represent overdevelopment of the site and would provide poor outlook, compromised privacy, inadequate amenity space, inadequate refuse storage space and potentially inadequate daylight resulting in substandard living conditions for prospective occupiers contrary to policies 3.5, 7A, 7B and 7D of the Ealing Development Management DPD (2013); policies 3.5 and 7.6 of the London Plan (2016); the Mayor's Housing SPG 2016; and the National Planning Policy Framework (2019). | The development by reason of its design, scale and siting in close proximity to the shared boundary would resulting in harm to the residential amenity of neighbouring residences due to an overbearing sense of enclosure and loss of light, contrary to policy 7B of the Ealing Development Management DPD (2013); policy 7.6 of the London Plan (2016 as amended) and the National Planning Policy Framework (2019)."
